Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:17.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}小さな思い出たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:23.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}両手いっぱい抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなただけ 想ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:34.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そんな時間(とき)がうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:39.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}どんなに離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:45.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}愛する気持ちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:51.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなたの隣にそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:57.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}寄り添っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:04.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そう 決して終わることのない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:10.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}本当の愛 見つけたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:16.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}「ずっとずっとそばにいます」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:21.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}誓ったあおい空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第九话 ～白妙～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.35,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 花菱君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,五木教授…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 对刚才的事有心理准备了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,努力写论文、帮忙是不错\N但要看清将来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我也会尽力帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好好努力 我对你很期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不对不对 不是为了说这个而叫你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉又开始说教了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友给的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都来帮忙 这个算是答谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,带女朋友一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊 薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能两个人出来 好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,时机真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,和葵小姐一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那、那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜和大学的朋友去摄影旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子和千香在收拾海滩小店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正好葵小姐也很无聊的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然说过很多次 葵小姐还是拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然说过很多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是中华街啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 肚子也饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难得来一次 得好好尝尝中华街的美味才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太贵的地方的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,甚、什么 小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我想尝尝那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,中国包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大的话还真吃不完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一起吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今次来的时候 真想让小葵吃好多好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,更要看清将来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,将来…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是电视台的外景拍摄什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,过去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚仪式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵穿结婚礼服的样子一定也非常漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的能带给小葵幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,接受许许多多人的祝福吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给 薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 小葵你不吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话雪糕也能两个人一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个年纪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,和小葵相遇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从那时起就一直想着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一直思念着一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是需要很大的勇气的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想到要是喜欢的人讨厌我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会变得非常的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那种感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一直困扰着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我除去了各种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让我自己充满了对薰少爷的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感到自己是如此地思念薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,感到自己是如此地喜欢薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要拥有喜欢薰少爷的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就非常幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,才能一直一心一意思念着薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从今以后也请一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请一直让我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一起住在外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一起住在外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎、怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,住在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 住在外面就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才去check in了（酒店入住手续）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是 那个…你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,突然说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没、 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,五木教授给了我招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然由犹豫过该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是想和小葵单独在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,房间比想象中的还要气派呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还附带这么丰盛的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那么 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是时钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为是普通的观览车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一成不变的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的这一瞬间只存在于眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,明天流动的将是不同的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,樱庭馆也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都住在同一屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都快乐地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是总有一天会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我想我们不得不接受那样的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 小葵 你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 你去那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,去给阿雅小姐打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我把和阿雅联络的事完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是打算吃完后再联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话 我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是我约你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我来说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太开心了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事吧 薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.95,0:13:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说了在外面过夜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面过夜！想都别想！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢啊 薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是被阿雅责骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之前 真想和薰少爷再多看看这夜景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真想向薰少爷再多撒娇一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都因为我 你被狠狠责骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我没做好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,给薰少爷添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,得到许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真、真的吗 薰少爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,开始还是反对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我和她谈了谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,允许你们在外过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 阿雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,葵小姐就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谈了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谈了有关小葵的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有关我的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我考虑过将来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想得最多的是小葵的幸福在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,自从定下婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一直思念着我的小葵的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该怎样来回应才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样做才能给小葵幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵的幸福既不在花菱家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也不在樱庭家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵的幸福在我自身之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是我的幸福里有小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵的幸福里有我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样互相包容就是我和小葵的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为了能够一直支持小葵\N我想我必须自己努力地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对于从作为未婚夫妻相遇的那刻起\N就一直喜欢我的小葵的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是让小葵得到幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,能这样为小葵着想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 房东小姐 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你看到的 烤地瓜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,着、着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个回来得正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 难道是烤地瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也来烤烤我们带回来的土产吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,土产？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对 是青花鱼干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,和地瓜一起烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 不见了 不见了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一定放在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,着、着火了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,葵蜜饯烤热后非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不准烤！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这青花鱼干是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看 是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,地瓜和青花鱼都已经占满地方了 放不下放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 说话不要像个小孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是小孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而且葵蜜饯当然是生吃味道最好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,烤烤也很好吃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 房东小姐 小鬼在欺负人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 要喝茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好
